<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77f01480-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460aaa–8"><num value="460aaa–8">§ 460aaa–8.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77f01481-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460aaa–8/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Acquisition of lands</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated an amount not to exceed $5,000,000 for the acquisition of land, interests in land, or structures within the national recreation area and on the mainland as needed for access and administrative facilities.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77f01482-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460aaa–8/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Other purposes</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In addition to the amounts authorized to be appropriated under subsection (a), there are authorized to be appropriated not more than $5,000,000 for development to carry out the other purposes of this subchapter.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id77f01483-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/292/s9">Pub. L. 101–292, § 9</ref>, <date date="1990-05-17">May 17, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/190">104 Stat. 190</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
